import React from 'react'

import {
    SidbarContainer,
    ClsIcon,
    CloseIcon
} from './SidebarElements'

const DropdoqnSidebar = () => {
    return (
        <DropdqnContainer>
            <ClsIcon>
                <CloseIcon/>
            </ClsIcon>
            <DropdqnWrap>
                <DropdqnMenu>
                    <DropdqnLink to="about">WHO WE ARE</DropdqnLink>
                    <DropdqnLink to="about">WHO WE ARE</DropdqnLink>
                    <DropdqnLink to="about">WHO WE ARE</DropdqnLink>
                    <DropdqnLink to="about">WHO WE ARE</DropdqnLink>
                    <DropdqnLink to="about">WHO WE ARE</DropdqnLink>
                </DropdqnMenu>
            </DropdqnWrap>
        </DropdqnContainer>
    )
}

export default DropdoqnSidebar;
